00:46:24,190 --> 00:46:27,090
It's only between me and Mr. No.

538
00:46:27,820 --> 00:46:30,559
I won't talk about it.

539
00:46:33,429 --> 00:46:34,559
You have a problem with Ji Wook.

540
00:46:35,829 --> 00:46:36,869
No, I don't.

541
00:46:38,630 --> 00:46:39,670
Ji Wook...

542
00:46:40,739 --> 00:46:42,000
