544
00:46:44,940 --> 00:46:45,969
No.

545
00:46:51,349 --> 00:46:52,409
You're right.

546
00:46:52,849 --> 00:46:53,920
To be honest,

547
00:46:54,650 --> 00:46:55,650
he's a bit strange.

548
00:46:57,250 --> 00:46:59,250
I think the case he's
working on now...

549
00:47:00,519 --> 00:47:04,059
must remind him
of his parents' incident.

550
00:47:05,659 --> 00:47:06,730
By the way,

551
00:47:07,260 --> 00:47:09,030
the same applies
for you too, Ms. Eun.

552
00:47:10,800 --> 00:47:14,039
My dad also passed away in a fire.

553
00:47:14,539 --> 00:47:15,670
But Ji Wook...

554
00:47:16,440 --> 00:47:18,340
was in the fire with them.

555
00:47:19,170 --> 00:47:21,010
