564
00:47:49,869 --> 00:47:51,510
On the list of the arsonists
in the district,

565
00:47:51,510 --> 00:47:54,079
Lee Joon Hae is only registered
for attempted arsons.

566
00:47:55,179 --> 00:47:57,250
Lee Joon Hae was in the video...

567
00:47:57,250 --> 00:47:59,280
of the fire on the day
of the incident,

568
00:47:59,280 --> 00:48:00,449
That's right,

569
00:48:00,449 --> 00:48:02,849
but it can't be used as evidence
to prove...

570
00:48:02,880 --> 00:48:03,920
his guilt.

