made by people like you.

673
00:55:53,050 --> 00:55:55,119
All I need is for you to become
a murderer.

674
00:55:58,630 --> 00:56:00,159
I'm not wrong.

675
00:56:00,960 --> 00:56:03,400
That means it is unacceptable to
make any kind of mistake...

676
00:56:03,969 --> 00:56:06,530
that could harm the order of
an organization,

677
00:56:06,530 --> 00:56:09,139
the order of the law,
and the order of power.

678
00:56:09,800 --> 00:56:13,139
We cannot afford to make a single
prosecution mistake whatsoever.

679
00:56:13,610 --> 00:56:14,639
Do you understand?

680
00:56:45,309 --> 00:56:47,309
Excuse me. I have to go somewhere.

681
00:56:48,139 --> 00:56:49,139
Okay.

682
00:57:07,760 --> 00:57:08,860
Hey, where are you?

