where you are.

684
00:57:12,800 --> 00:57:15,599
I'll be right there. Okay.

685
00:57:22,239 --> 00:57:23,750
I want to eat tteokbokki.

686
00:57:24,880 --> 00:57:25,949
Tteokbokki?

687
00:57:27,250 --> 00:57:28,320
Do you want to?

688
00:57:29,050 --> 00:57:30,619
- Here?
- Of course.

689
00:57:32,420 --> 00:57:33,489
- Just wait here for a little bit.
- What?

690
00:57:33,489 --> 00:57:36,389
I'll buy you tteokbokki, sundae,
gimbap, and everything else.

691
00:57:36,389 --> 00:57:38,690
- I can...
- Wait here. I'll be right back.

692
00:57:52,139 --> 00:57:53,610
How does it taste? Is it delicious?

